column5: I know there are a few of our group on this board periodically. Here is a video to get their appetite going. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pLYYpbILr4c
LOL.....watched it yesterday. You faded away from my fish too early! LOL
All I know is ----- I'm suddenly hungry
LOl, yeah my editing skills have a little to be desired. Also a little shaky on some of the zooms.
The song is perfect and I am really hungry.
Were they flying more beer into camp or were there just two of you?
